'''Clone Wars Connecting the Dots''' is a ten-minute documentary created for the [[Star Wars: Clone Wars Volume Two|''Star Wars: Clone Wars'' Volume Two]] DVD. It features [[Genndy Tartakovsky]] and the crew of ''[[Star Wars: Clone Wars]]'' explaining how they managed to tie the series to [[Star Wars: Episode II Attack of the Clones|''Attack of the Clones'']] and [[Star Wars: Episode III Revenge of the Sith|''Revenge of the Sith'']].

